  <title>Smart sanitizer dispenser using Arduino </title>
<subsection xml:id="subsec-Introduction-sanitizer">
  <title>Introduction </title>
  <p>
    Hand sanitizer is an antiseptic liquid which is used to kill the germs. In this pandemic situation sanitizer plays a major role to save us from the virus. WHO instructs the people, to wash their hands for more than 20 seconds to kill the corona virus. We often use sanitizer in public places, there might be a situation to use the sanitizer which is also used by the infected person that may increase the risk of transmitting the viruses so easily. To avoid this kind of situation, automatic sanitizer will detect the person’s hand when the hand is place before the sanitizer and it will dispense the sanitizer without human’s touch. This prototype model will be used as touch free sanitizer to avoid the spread of corona virus. In this prototype IR sensor is used.
  </p>
  <image source="/images/sanitizer.jpg" width="40%"/>
</subsection>
